| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1297 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 198b36ed-d8af-5f6c-bd9b-d5fc47462e75"
